{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"每个诽谤者、造谣者将遭严惩真活该！"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他[诽谤者、造谣者]聚集财富并[经常]计算，"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他认为他的财富能使他永生[注]。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"绝不可能！他必将被投入毁灭之坑中。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你怎能知道毁灭之坑是什么？"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"那是安拉的燃烧着的烈火，"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"它能烧入[人的]心里。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他们必将被关闭在其中，"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"被捆在长柱上烧灼。"}]}